        "metaDescription": "Discover 10 compelling reasons why Utpala Cafe is the best cafe in Boudha, Kathmandu. From organic vegetarian food to peaceful ambiance, see what makes this cafe #1.",
        "urlSlug": "/10-reasons-utpala-cafe-best-cafe-boudha",
